latestPosts.caption:
Bangalore based Candid Wedding photographer 📸 : @journeysbyvivek with the experience of having shot 400+ weddings across cultures, religions & borders since 2015.
We are a company made up of young individuals where Art & Passion takes Center stage & everything else is secondary. Almost all of us left our corporate/ Engineering careers to pursue what our hearts truly desired which was to tell beautiful stories of people & we realised what better avenue than weddings to do it. And that is how our team was founded.
So, reach out to us to have your big day captured in the most genuine & honest way possible
.
Our super fun Power couple 🔥
Sparsha // Karthik
